item.dc:creator: @decrepify decrepify
item.description:
@decrepify wrote:

Try editing the run to whatever jdk version you have.

This usually means that the jdk or jre file thats already in there from the previous coder or releaser had a different java version then you
To find out what jre or jdk you have go to C:\Program Files\Java

Hope this helped
